ROAD SAFETY MANAGEMENT USING MODERN TECHNOLOGIES
The main source of information on the condition of transportation processes is the timely technologies of
discovering the discrepancy between the quality of transportation processes implementation and their design indices.
This requires the organization of continuous control of current condition with the necessary requirement of minimum
